  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>JUMP AND DODGE UNTILL THE LEVEL COMPLETE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Avoid dangerous traps</strong> with <strong>clever jumps</strong> and <strong>right timings</strong>. Be <strong>vigilant</strong>,<strong> calculate each step</strong>, <strong>remember</strong> <strong>all</strong> the<strong> mistakes and</strong> <strong>don't repeat them again. </strong> Embark on a <strong>journey worth remembering </strong>and<strong> take your friends with you.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Happy Sawland is waiting for you:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> ▪ 4 Chapters: Calm Meadows, Castle of Perseverance, Cold Winter of Awaiting, Magic Lands of Awareness</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ 40 Levels with unique layouts</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ 2 Difficulties: Discovery and Doubt</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ Play alone</strong> or <strong>with your friends</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/c270bad4e21d656736dad23d8ec2db15.poster.avif?t=1759071022\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/c270bad4e21d656736dad23d8ec2db15.webm?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/c270bad4e21d656736dad23d8ec2db15.mp4?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>THESE MEADOWS SEEM TOO CALM. WHAT PLACES DO THEY LEAD TO?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/449643f5ebb005f1079e08a1ca5e82cc.poster.avif?t=1759071022\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/449643f5ebb005f1079e08a1ca5e82cc.webm?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/449643f5ebb005f1079e08a1ca5e82cc.mp4?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>WHAT IS PROTECTED BY THIS CASTLE AND WHAT IS BEYOND?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/e3fe2781c287ee603e7753736fd2bab1.poster.avif?t=1759071022\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/e3fe2781c287ee603e7753736fd2bab1.webm?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/e3fe2781c287ee603e7753736fd2bab1.mp4?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>WHAT AWAITS BEHIND THESE COLD AND FROZEN LANDS?</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/146b73830e658b17da018f3c500d4366.poster.avif?t=1759071022\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/146b73830e658b17da018f3c500d4366.webm?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/146b73830e658b17da018f3c500d4366.mp4?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>SHOULD I GO THERE? OR MAYBE JUMP HERE? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The sun is gone</strong>. All <strong>levels turn pitch black</strong>, you hear <strong>a distant</strong> familiar <strong>tone</strong>, it <strong>beckons you</strong>. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Would you take on the challenge or doubt yourself?</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ Doubt </strong>every step!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ </strong>Welcome to the <strong>Indecision, Hesitation</strong> and L<strong>ack of Certainty</strong>!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ </strong>Welcome to the <strong>\"Doubt\" Difficulty</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/f7fad06cb27588065ea10d9ac16b92ee.poster.avif?t=1759071022\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/f7fad06cb27588065ea10d9ac16b92ee.webm?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/f7fad06cb27588065ea10d9ac16b92ee.mp4?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TAKE YOUR FRIENDS WITH YOU</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ Play</strong> all <strong>4 chapters</strong> and <strong>40 levels</strong> <strong>with</strong> <strong>your friends</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▪ Overcome</strong> the <strong>hardships together</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Happy Sawland</strong> <strong>invites everyone</strong>.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/02dd3c43a4bc43c8c33f2d9eedb064e2.poster.avif?t=1759071022\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/02dd3c43a4bc43c8c33f2d9eedb064e2.webm?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962150/extras/02dd3c43a4bc43c8c33f2d9eedb064e2.mp4?t=1759071022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
